description:
playback-controller.ts:82 — setSpeed(0) causes delay = duration/0 = Infinity, silently freezing the animation forever. setSpeed(-1) causes delay = -400, which browsers clamp to 0, running all steps instantly. The UI speed buttons (0.25x-4x) prevent this, but the controller has no internal guard.

Fix: Clamp speed to [0.1, 10] range in setSpeed():
```
setSpeed(speed: number) {
  this.speed = Math.max(0.1, Math.min(10, speed));
  ...
}
```
